  "description": {
   "en": "The world has become a desolate, lawless land where bandits roam free, innocent people suffer, and demons lurk around every corner. Sona Yuki is traveling with his family when they are attacked by bandits. His entire family is murdered, and he is left with a snake mark on his hand. As he is about to die, a woman comes up to him and gives him an option: continue to live in this harsh environment or die peacefully now. Yuki chooses life and Garami, the woman, gives him a second chance at life in exchange for his servitude. Garami is a weapons merchant and a gun for hire that travels from town to town for clients. Yuki sees how brutal and unforgiving this world can truly be.",
   "id": "Keluarga Sona, petani pionir, diserang gerombolan bandit bernama Hydra. Selain melihat keluarganya dibunuh di depan matanya, tangan Sona dicap dan dibiarkan di gurun. \n\nSaat sudah pasrah untuk mati, muncullah seorang wanita cantik misterius. Wanita itu adalah Garamy, Arms Peddler. Kini, petualangan Sona dan Garamy dimulai!",
   "it": "La famiglia di Sona, figlio di coloni, è assalita dalla banda di Hydra. Il ragazzo è costretto a vedere i suoi cari barbaramente massacrati davanti ai proprio occhi e, dopo che gli è stato impresso sulla mano un marchio, viene abbandonato nel deserto...\n\nOrmai rassegnato allla morte, gli compare una misteriosa e bellissima donna. E' Galamy, la commerciante d'armi nomade. Lei gli fornisce acqua e gli vende, al prezzo di un pendente ricordo della madre, un'arma. Inizia così una nuova ballata di vendetta...",
   "ja": "生死の代価を轍に刻む、スティグマ・ファンタジー！！\n\n開拓民の子ソーナの家族が極悪非道なハイドラ一味に襲われる。家族を目の前で惨殺されたうえ、手に焼きゴテの烙印を押され砂漠に捨てられたソーナ。死を覚悟した時、現れたる謎の美女。その名は武器商人ガラミィ――。彼女は、ソーナの身柄を代価に水を与え、母の遺品であるペンダントを代価に武器を売る。復讐がための剣を手にしたソーナの冒険が始まった――。"
  },
